---
// src/pages/vision.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-20">

        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mb-8 text-center animate-fade-in text-white">
            Our Vision
        </h1>

        <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto mb-12 text-center animate-fade-in-delay-1">
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-blue-400 leading-relaxed">
                To create an open community where talent gathers, startups are born and the future of Europe's AI is built
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto space-y-6 text-white/85 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-delay-2">
            <p>
                North Star AGI started as a community focused on the engineers, the innovators, and those with the drive but without the resources.
            </p>
            <p>
                We highlight local talent and share the latest knowledge in the world of AI and robotics.
            </p>
            <p>
                Why do this? During the many AI talks here in Antwerp, questions that often come up are: "Is Europe behind in AI?" and "What do you think about Europe and the AI race?"
            </p>
            <p>
                North Star AGI is our answer to this. We are laying the foundations for a strong Belgium and Europe.
            </p>
            <p>
                We started from scratch and alone, but we started, and now people with the same vision are joining and learning about us.
            </p>
            <p>
                Everyone has a spark of ambition in their blood; the friction around us keeps suppressing it. North Star finds a way to fight nonetheless.
            </p>
            <p>
                We're all in this together. A community doesn't exist without its people, and we need you.
            </p>
            <p>
                Europe's springtime is coming. The ecosystems are waking up, and a sense of urgency is spreading.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl font-medium text-blue-400">
                It's now or never.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto mt-12 text-center animate-fade-in-delay-3">
            <p class="text-white/85 text-lg mb-6">Join our community:</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
                <a href="https://discord.gg/m5Hknymurb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                   class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
